column1:
US-2: I would like to play more than one game
at a time
US-3: I would like to leave games at any time
US-4: I would like to create a match

US-5: I would like to be able to receive invitations
to games

US-6: I would like to be able to send more than
one invitation

US-7: I would like to be able to register to the
platform

US-8: I would like to be able to unregister from
the platform

US-9: I would like pieces to disappear when they
are captured
US-10: I would like to be able to play Banqi online

US-14: I would like to know if I won or lost the 
game
US-15: I would like to know when a game is over

US-16: I would like to see a record of all the
games I've played

US-17: I would like to be able to save my current
game state

US-18: I would like to be able to reload saved
games

US-26: I woud like to be able to flip a piece over
for my turn
US-27: I would like to be able to move my pieces

US-28: I would like to be able to capture enemy
pieces

US-36: I would like to be able to login to my 
account that I registered with

US-40: I would like to be able to view my profile 
for the account I created

US-42: I would like to be able to play Banqi with 
friends.

US-43: I would like to be able to come back to 
my game

US-44: I would like to be able to view my game 
statistics on my profile page
